I didn't want you to go for her.

1286
01:00:16,988 --> 01:00:18,615
- Right?
- Yeah.

1287
01:00:19,282 --> 01:00:21,784
I'll say this because it's you, Aru.

1288
01:00:23,745 --> 01:00:25,747
She likes older men.

1289
01:00:26,664 --> 01:00:28,041
And men with beards.

1290
01:00:28,541 --> 01:00:29,417
She said that.

1291
01:00:32,712 --> 01:00:34,130
I don't have a beard.

1292
01:00:34,631 --> 01:00:36,716
I'll share that information with you.

1293
01:00:36,799 --> 01:00:39,385
I don't think there's any need
for me to hide that.

1294
01:00:42,055 --> 01:00:43,556
So that's that.

1295
01:00:45,808 --> 01:00:48,770
- Atsushi is a fair man.
- Yeah. He's an athlete.

1296
01:00:48,853 --> 01:00:49,771
Good sportsmanship.

1297
01:00:49,854 --> 01:00:51,731
And Aru seems so happy again.

1298
